---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="About Us | Free Resume Builder" description="Learn about ResumeBuilder - our mission to help professionals create standout resumes for free.">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.25rem">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:2.5rem">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.25rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:0.75rem;letter-spacing:-0.02em">About Us</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.0625rem;color:var(--gray-500);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto">Making professional resume tools accessible to everyone, everywhere.</p>
    </div>

    <article style="color:var(--gray-600);font-size:0.9375rem;line-height:1.8">
      <p style="font-size:1.0625rem;color:var(--gray-500);margin-bottom:2rem;line-height:1.7">ResumeBuilder is a free, online resume creation tool designed to help job seekers build professional, ATS-friendly resumes quickly and easily. Our mission is to remove barriers between talented professionals and their dream jobs.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--gray-900);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;letter-spacing:-0.02em">Our Story</h2>
      <p>ResumeBuilder was created to solve a simple problem: existing resume builders were either too expensive, too complicated, or produced resumes that Applicant Tracking Systems couldn't read. We believed everyone deserves access to a tool that creates beautiful, scannable resumes without requiring design skills or a subscription.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--gray-900);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;letter-spacing:-0.02em">What Makes Us Different</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;margin:1.5rem 0">
        <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
          <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.375rem">100% Free</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);margin:0;line-height:1.5">No hidden fees, no credit card required. All templates and features are completely free.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
          <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.375rem">ATS-Friendly</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);margin:0;line-height:1.5">Our templates are optimized for Applicant Tracking Systems, ensuring your resume gets seen by recruiters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
          <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.375rem">Multiple Templates</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);margin:0;line-height:1.5">Choose from Classic, Modern, Professional, and Creative designs to match your industry.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
          <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.375rem">Privacy First</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);margin:0;line-height:1.5">Your data stays on your device. We never store or share your personal information.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--gray-900);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;letter-spacing:-0.02em">Our Values</h2>
      <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.75rem">
        <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;align-items:flex-start"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">Accessibility:</span><span>Making professional resume tools available to everyone, everywhere.</span></li>
        <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;align-items:flex-start"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">Simplicity:</span><span>Removing complexity so you can focus on what matters — your content.</span></li>
        <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;align-items:flex-start"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">Quality:</span><span>Ensuring every template meets professional standards and ATS requirements.</span></li>
        <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;align-items:flex-start"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">Privacy:</span><span>Protecting your data with a privacy-first, client-side architecture.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div style="background:var(--gray-50);border-top:1px solid var(--gray-200);border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray-200);padding:3rem 1.5rem">
    <div style="max-width:960px;margin:0 auto">
      <h3 style="font-size:1.125rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:1.25rem;text-align:center">Free Career Tools</h3>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(130px,1fr));gap:0.75rem">
        <a href="/" class="card card-hover" style="padding:1rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;text-align:center">
          <span style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--primary-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg></span>
          <span style="font-size:0.8125rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray-700)">Resume Builder</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/ats-score" class="card card-hover" style="padding:1rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;text-align:center">
          <span style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--primary-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/></svg></span>
          <span style="font-size:0.8125rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray-700)">ATS Score</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/cover-letter" class="card card-hover" style="padding:1rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;text-align:center">
          <span style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--primary-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg></span>
          <span style="font-size:0.8125rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray-700)">Cover Letter</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/resume-examples" class="card card-hover" style="padding:1rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;text-align:center">
          <span style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--primary-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg></span>
          <span style="font-size:0.8125rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray-700)">Examples</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/templates" class="card card-hover" style="padding:1rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;text-align:center">
          <span style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--primary-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/></svg></span>
          <span style="font-size:0.8125rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray-700)">Templates</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>